headline: Molina (MOH) Beats Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Molina (MOH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 3.75% and 0.24%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: The Cigna Group Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of The Cigna Group (NYSE: CI) today declared a cash dividend of $1.51 per share of its common stock, payable on June 18, 2025 to shareholders of record as of the close of business on June 3, 2025.
